{"tid":1076452,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"應該先辭職後搵工定搵左先辭？","createTime":"2019-03-25T00:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T00:26:13.000Z","uid":15806,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0d5322c7584b31e686ce48e319b9cd523365a4","tid":1076452,"uid":15806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"而家呢份工做左一排已經頂唔順個上司<br />\n冇人知佢想點 但要求多又五時花六時變<br />\n上司好鍾諗搞到啲野勁趕 然後就叫啲同事ot陪佢清晒啲野<br />\n每日都返到好攰 開始搵緊工走 但send完都冇咩消息<br />\n到底應該先辭職後搵工定搵左先辭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbb9b702641e7986f1a1b74494882c7f8975659","tid":1076452,"uid":196924,"like":87,"dislike":13,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"辭咗先<br />\n返緊工有回音你請假見工仲煩"},{"pid":"d4181578cfc9f5dbc9b76ec05b8bd1011093cbb7","tid":1076452,"uid":51250,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"一定係搵咗先<br />\nsick leave見工就可以"},{"pid":"e88d89d5981fcf3fd5274c7cf04169b5c3c6dc40","tid":1076452,"uid":188148,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:38:31.000Z","msg":"正常應該搵左先<br />\n除非真係好難頂"},{"pid":"1d47baf97a2e6469ac3e61af687960a446e0600b","tid":1076452,"uid":55386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好想裸辭"},{"pid":"b289755048c7683d8578b38af9c4151ff310fa02","tid":1076452,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":24,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6bea222c064e340782dab701193d1eaad60a47d","tid":1076452,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:42:23.000Z","msg":"成個月通知期 <br />\n都冇回音嘅話應該諗下自己有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24be5a2244f773aa7cc90c4c24f29191080c042f","tid":1076452,"uid":15806,"like":0,"dislike":2