"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"呢份工同個上司都好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\not又冇錢"},{"pid":"0f0a0d40d5691051659d403d602750816d9b2af4","tid":1076452,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:48:14.000Z","msg":"唔好裸辭<br />\n反正你都唔做<br />\n見工sl咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我試過一星期見幾次如果要返工唔知點sl"},{"pid":"1cdbd042e9d78e8a25bd5cd6b2c6dc3d1cf658bd","tid":1076452,"uid":83094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99b644fe6a2b8ab1c2e55fa626ce91b5fe44abe9","tid":1076452,"uid":197416,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"上個月尾開始send cv<br />\n今個月月頭請左日假去見工<br />\n兩日後就決定遞信 有冇offer都照走<br />\n點知遞信當日就收offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4月頭last day<br />\n4月中翻新工<br />\n中間仲夠時間去個旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f78f6d48928b5c3742e7b76bfe11091ddf397f","tid":1076452,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c58095101936736eb4405ad58e8cfbb752eaacd","tid":1076452,"uid":71740,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:29:50.000Z","msg":"至少都一個月通知期，搵咗先辭新公司點等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"要間新公司等你就得<br />\n但等你期間可能佢又會in左堆人<br />\n入面有個勁嘅人就收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過辭左職果個月開始搵無壞嘅<br />\n你應該都了解自己果行請人情況<br />\n我自己做緊果行有d舊同事係比公司炒走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過兩個星期搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d865512c